让我惊讶的是仅仅14厘米的船舵

81
00:03:33.019 --> 00:03:35.371
I could control four meters of absorbent.
就能控制四米长的吸收材料

82
00:03:35.371 --> 00:03:39.187
Then I was so happy that I kept playing with the robot,
我非常高兴能一直摆弄这个小机器

83
00:03:39.187 --> 00:03:41.651
and so you see the robot has
你能看到这只机器船

84
00:03:41.651 --> 00:03:43.323
a front rudder here.
有一个舵在前面

85
00:03:43.323 --> 00:03:44.539
Normally it's at the back.
正常的话它应该在后面

86
00:03:44.539 --> 00:03:48.154
And, playing, I realized that the maneuverability
我摆弄它的时候注意到

87
00:03:48.154 --> 00:03:49.434
of this was really amazing,
它的可控性是惊人的

88
00:03:49.434 --> 00:03:51.362
and I could avoid an obstacle at the very last second,
我能在最后一秒躲开一个障碍物

89
00:03:51.362 --> 00:03:53.034
more maneuverable than a normal boat.
它比一般的船可控性更强

90
00:03:53.034 --> 00:03:55.898
Then I started publishing online, and
接着我开始在网上发布

91
00:03:55.898 --> 00:03:58.810
some friends from Korea, they started being
一些来自韩国的朋友开始对这项发明感兴趣

92
00:03:58.810 --> 00:04:00.539
interested in this, and we made a boat
所以我们又做了一艘船

93
00:04:00.539 --> 00:04:02.347
which has a front rudder and a back rudder,
它前面后面都有船舵

94
00:04:02.347 --> 00:04:04.405
so we started interacting with this,
所以我们开始与它互动

95
00:04:04.405 --> 00:04:06.524
and it was slightly better,
它又变好了一点

96
00:04:06.524 --> 00:04:08.448
although it was very small and a bit off balance,
尽管它很小还有一点不平衡

97
00:04:08.448 --> 00:04:09.528
but then we thought,
但之后我们想

98
00:04:09.528 --> 00:04:11.416
what if we have more than two points of control?
我们再多加一些控制点会怎样呢？

99
00:04:11.416 --> 00:04:13.408
What if the entire boat becomes a point of control?
如果整艘船变成一个控制点会怎样呢？

100
00:04:13.408 --> 00:04:15.528
What if the entire boat changes shape?
整艘船的形状能够改变会怎样呢？

101
00:04:15.528 --> 00:04:17.968
So — (Applause)
所以--（掌声）

102
00:04:17.968 --> 00:04:19.864
Thank you very much. (Applause)
非常感谢（掌声）

103
00:04:19.864 --> 00:04:22.449
And so that's the beginning of Protei,
这就是Protei的开始

104
00:04:22.449 --> 00:04:24.088
and that's the first boat in history
这是历史上第一艘

105
00:04:24.088 --> 00:04:25.712
that completely changed the shape of the hull
能够完全改变船身形状的船

106
00:04:25.712 --> 00:04:26.882
in order to control it,
这是为了能更好的控制它

107
00:04:26.882 --> 00:04:29.768
and the properties of sailing that we get
这艘帆船的性能

108
00:04:29.768 --> 00:04:32.666
are very superior compared to a normal boat.
也比一般的船好得多

109
00:04:32.666 --> 00:04:35.320
When we're turning, we have the feeling of surfing,
当我们转向的时候， 我们有一种冲浪的感觉

110
00:04:35.320 --> 00:04:39.436
and the way it's going up-wind, it's very efficient.
还有它逆风航行的时候，它非常高效

111
00:04:39.436 --> 00:04:42.136
This is low speed, low wind speed,
这是低速--低风速的状态

112
00:04:42.136 --> 00:04:44.209
and the maneuverability is very increased,
可控性提高了很多

113
00:04:44.209 --> 00:04:46.520
and here I'm going to do a small jibe,
我来做个小转向

114
00:04:46.520 --> 00:04:48.616
and look at the position of the sail.
看帆的位置

115
00:04:48.616 --> 00:04:52.216
What's happening is that, because the boat changes shape,
现在，因为船身变形了

116
00:04:52.216 --> 00:04:54.556
the position of the front sail and the main sail
前帆的位置和主控帆的位置

117
00:04:54.556 --> 00:04:55.733
are different to the wind.
对风向来说是不同的

118
00:04:55.733 --> 00:04:57.616
We're catching wind from both sides.
我们在两个方向都兜住了风

119
00:04:57.616 --> 00:04:59.875
And this is exactly what we're looking [for]
这正是我们所期待的

120
00:04:59.875 --> 00:05:01.659
if we want to pull something long and heavy.
如果我们需要拉动一些又长又重的东西

121
00:05:01.659 --> 00:05:04.048
We don't want to lose pulling power, nor direction.
我们就既不能失去拉动力也不能失去方向

122
00:05:04.048 --> 00:05:06.888
So, I wanted to know if this was possible
所以我想知道有没有可能

123
00:05:06.888 --> 00:05:08.359
to put this at an industrial level,
把它投入工业化生产

124
00:05:08.359 --> 00:05:10.871
so we made a large boat with a large sail,
所以我们做了一艘有更大的帆的船

125
00:05:10.871 --> 00:05:13.567
and with a very light hull, inflatable,
它的船身非常轻，充气式的

126
00:05:13.567 --> 00:05:15.072
very small footprint,
在水面激起的涟漪很小

127
00:05:15.072 --> 00:05:17.896
so we have a very big size and power ratio.
我们的船尺寸很大而且动力很强

128
00:05:17.896 --> 00:05:21.127
After this, we wanted to see if we could
这之后， 我们想看看我们能否

129
00:05:21.127 --> 00:05:23.424
implement this and automate the system,
实施并实现系统的自动化

130
