00:07:34.300 --> 00:07:36.319
you might create what we call lateral lift,
你将会造成我们所谓的侧面上升

182
00:07:36.319 --> 00:07:39.244
so we could get further or closer to the wind.
所以我们就能走的更远或者更接近风

