00:11:01.134 --> 00:11:03.464
They made it, but they eventually published
他们将它制造出来，但他们最终

264
00:11:03.464 --> 00:11:04.588
a simplified design.
发布了一个简单的设计

265
00:11:04.588 --> 00:11:06.517
They also made it into an Instructable,
他们也把它发布在Instructable上

266
00:11:06.517 --> 00:11:08.252
and in less than one week, they had
不到一星期，他们就有

267
00:11:08.252 --> 00:11:11.012
almost 10,000 views, and they got many new friends.
将近一万次浏览，而且他们交到很多新朋友

268
00:11:11.012 --> 00:11:13.916
We're working on also simpler technology,
我们正在研发的也是简单的科技

269
00:11:13.916 --> 00:11:15.867
not that complex, with younger people
不是特别复杂，我们中有年轻人

270
00:11:15.867 --> 00:11:17.436
and also older people,
也有老人

271
00:11:17.436 --> 00:11:20.587
like this dinosaur is from Mexico. (Laughter)
就像这只来自墨西哥的恐龙（笑声）

272
00:11:20.587 --> 00:11:23.404
So Protei is now an international network
所以Protei 项目现在是一个全球性的

273
00:11:23.404 --> 00:11:26.252
of innovation for selling technology
利用这个变形船身

274
00:11:26.252 --> 00:11:28.044
using this shape-shifting hull.
来销售科技的创新网络

275
00:11:28.044 --> 00:11:32.079
And what puts us together is that we have a common,
让我们聚在一起的

276
00:11:32.079 --> 00:11:34.868
at least, global understanding
是对“商业”这个词的相同的全球性理解

277
00:11:34.868 --> 00:11:37.940
