来控制很多这些机器

326
00:13:44.434 --> 00:13:46.185
to monitor coral reefs
去监测珊瑚礁

327
00:13:46.185 --> 00:13:48.324
or to monitor fisheries.
去监控鱼群

328
00:13:48.324 --> 00:13:52.814
Our hope is that we can use open hardware technology
我们希望可以用硬件开源技术

329
00:13:52.814 --> 00:13:56.345
